name: Portrait of a Poet (video)
description:
A visual narrative about one of my favorite artist/models I've painted. She is a romantic poet. I wanted to paint something to reflect that. I added a contrasting combo of thorns and cherry blossoms to represent the desire and pain of love, a theme she often expresses.

model: Roxanne Huber
photo and body paint by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
